Tablet Skin for Squeezebox Server
=================================

This is a skin for the Logitech Squeezebox server. It is intended to be a reasonably lightweight skin that works nicely on the Apple iPad.

This version has been tested on the v7.5.x series of Squeezebox Server.

Changes for v1.2
------------------

* Improved autocomplete popup for Settings.
* Moved the Server Settings and Player Settings items from the home page footer to 'gear' icons.

The Code
--------

The Tablet folder contains the skin.

The Publish folder contains the files required for publishing the skin as a Squeezebox Server plugin.


